what_are:
  title: What Are Data Marts?
  content: |-
    Data Marts are specialized repositories that focus on specific areas of interest within your organization. Organized within broader data domains, they consolidate information from multiple sources into a streamlined, accessible structure. By storing only the most relevant data for specific user groups, data marts make analysis efficient, insightful, and impactful.
